data.description: Completely Transformed Home Ready for You to Embrace! Step into a beautifully updated haven and relish in the modern amenities it has to offer. The enchanting 1900's original staircase pairs seamlessly with the luxury of an ensuite bathroom for the primary bedroom. Experience the joy of an open-concept kitchen and family room with stainless steel appliances, a convenient eat-on bar, stylish open shelving, and a laundry room right at your fingertips. The main floor boasts a spacious 15x15 bedroom, while two additional bedrooms and baths are nestled upstairs. Outside, you'll find off-street parking with new asphalt, a generously-sized fenced flat rear yard, and a delightful wrap-around porch perfect for cherished gatherings with loved ones. Don't miss your chance to get this move in ready home with so many updates.
